00:42:54.718 --> 00:42:58.498
and describe CAR T cell progress. My disclosures

701
00:42:59.098 --> 00:42:59.378
are here.

702
00:43:01.010 --> 00:43:04.830
I wanted to step back on this issue over the last 20

