00:43:08.930 --> 00:43:12.910
34% decline in cancer death rates.

705
00:43:13.090 --> 00:43:13.350
And

706
00:43:14.330 --> 00:43:18.210
a lot of this is due now to checkpoint therapies, T-cell engagers,

707
00:43:18.270 --> 00:43:18.410
and

708
00:43:19.350 --> 00:43:22.950
cell therapies. So immunotherapy has had a huge impact

709
00:43:23.590 --> 00:43:25.930
on cancer survivorship.

710
00:43:27.550 --> 00:43:31.430
And to link in with what you just saw from Charles Sawyers, it's a 25-year

711
00:43:31.510 --> 00:43:34.750
anniversary since the first targeted

712
00:43:35.010 --> 00:43:37.330
