713
00:43:38.270 --> 00:43:39.480
in leukemia,

714
00:43:41.390 --> 00:43:42.790
to inhibit a kinase.

715
00:43:44.370 --> 00:43:45.750
And if you look back

716
00:43:46.670 --> 00:43:50.550
centuries ago, Cicero, two years before he was assassinated by

